{"title":"有感于坚持两手抓","authors":["梁必业"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":5,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"有感于坚持两手抓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁必业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持唯物论，运用辩证法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个文明建设一起抓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义路，富民强国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四项原则支撑固大厦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物质是基础，精神力量大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物质精神相依互转化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切忌片面性，思想莫僵化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实事求是决策定计划。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多干实际事，不说空泛话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功夫用在研究和调查。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方针政策对，风正好方法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全面领导坚持两手抓。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}